Exterior Street, between West 230th Street and West Kingsbridge Road. The view is in a southwesterly direction, showing W.P.A. men working on a sewer project. In the center background is visible the Webb Academy; on the extreme right is the Hall of Fame of New York University, and in the left background is the U.S. Veterans Hospital.

April 27, 1936.
